Title: Hands-On with Profiles: 'One of the All-Time Most Requested VS Code Features' -- Visual Studio Magazine
Description: In announcing the latest Visual Studio Code update last week, Microsoft said the new profiles functionality was one of the all-time most-requested Visual Studio Code features, allowing for unique configurations for different projects and workspaces.
